These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding, surfing
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | surfing | skateboarding | rugby |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: cabbage, carrot, watermelon
1. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating cabbage is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | cabbage | watermelon | carrot |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | board-games | drawing | magic-tricks |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, jazz, techno
1. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | country | techno | jazz |

